title: Pre-UFYB 22: It's Not About You – How to Stop Taking Sh*t Personally
itunes:title: Pre-UFYB 22: It's Not About You – How to Stop Taking Sh*t Personally
description:
Today, I explain the importance of not taking things personally and I prove to you that what other people choose to do means absolutely NOTHING about you. Tune in to find out what you can start doing today to stop taking someone else’s actions personally and dramatically improve your romantic and professional life.

Get full show notes and more information here: http://bit.ly/2yGLzr3
